CatDescriptText: Bethel A.M.E. Church on 1206 Wylie Avenue, now torn down.  Next to the church on left is an 'Old Furniture' store at 1210 -1208  Wylie Avenue, and a laundromat on the far left.
TitMainTitle: Exterior view of Bethel AME Church, Wylie Avenue at Elm Street, Hill District
